hopobject.body: I'm on work experience crazy bulk uk coupon I actually believe Zimmerman would've followed a white kid who was dressed the same way Martin was dressed. That's where the profiling came in. Not by race, but by fashion. If you listen to the dispatchers tapes, Zimmerman wasn't even certain that the suspect was black until after he called in. When the dispatcher asks for a description, he pauses for a couple of seconds, then says "uuhh, I think he's black".
